description:
If someone tells you something that seems far fetched, you may ask for evidence. Proof is valuable in our society to validate our beliefs and theories. In this second lecture of this series, Wes Peppers goes through concrete facts to reveal the truth in the Bible and he presents proof the Bible is true from external sources. Proving the Bible true is difficult, especially with atheism on the rise in our modern world. There is, however, mounting historical factual data to support the veracity of Jesus and all of His works.

For more, please visit:
https://amazingdiscoveries.org
https://amazingdiscoveries.tv
